               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     4ra-87va)
 I-1) Introduction (fol. 4ra-7va)
 I-2) Homily by Timothy
                     (Damātewos), Patriarch [of Alexandria] for the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 7va-15va);
                     miracle (fols. 15va-16vb); commemorative notice (fols. 16vb-17rb); ʾarke-hymn
                     (fol. 17rb)
 I-3) Homily by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs the Orthodox for the 12th
                     of Tāḫśāś [Miyāzyā] (fols. 17rb-22ra); miracle (fol. 22ra-vb); commemorative
                     notice (fol. 23ra-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 23va)
 I-4) Homily by an anonymous
                     author for the 12th of Ṭǝrr [Tāḫśāś] (fols. 23vb-29va); miracle (fol.
                     29va-30ra); commemorative notice (fol. 30rb-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 30va)
                     I-5) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of Yakkātit (fols. 30va-34ra);
                     miracle (fol. 34ra-vb); commemorative notice (fol. 35ra-rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol.
                     35rb)
 I-6) Homily by Yoḥannǝs [Severus], Metropolitan [Patriarch] of
                     Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 35rb-50ra); miracle (fols.
                     50ra-51rb); commemorative notice (fol. 51rb-va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 51va)
                     I-7) Homily [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for the 12th of Miyāzyā
                     [Ṭǝrr] (fols. 51va-57ra); miracle (fols. 57ra-58va); commemorative notice (fol.
                     58va-vb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 58vb-59ra)
 I-8) Homily by Yoḥannǝs,
                     Metropolitan of Ethiopia for Gǝnbot (fols. 59ra-60va); miracle (fols.
                     60va-61vb); commemorative notice (fols. 61vb-62ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol.
                     62ra-rb)
 I-9) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, Metropolitan of Aksum (ʾAkʷǝsum) for
                     Sane (fols. 62rb-67va); miracle (fols. 67vb-68vb); commemorative notice (fols.
                     68vb-69va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 69va)
 I-10) Homily by Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs
                     for Ḥamle (fols. 69va-73vb); miracle (fols. 73vb-74va); commemorative notice
                     (fols. 74va-75ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 75ra)
 I-11) Homily by an anonymous
                     author for Naḥāse (fols. 75ra-78ra); miracle (fol. 78ra-vb); commemorative
                     notice (fols. 78vb-79ra); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 79ra)
 I-12) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for Maskaram (fols. 79ra-81vb); miracle (fols. 81vb-82ra);
                     commemorative notice (fol. 82rb); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 82rb-va)
 I-13) Homily
                     by an anonymous author for Ṭǝqǝmt (fols. 82va-86va); miracle (fol. 86va-vb);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 86vb-87va); ʾarke-hymn (fol. 87va)
 I-14)
                     Account of the eschatological war between Archangel Michael and Satan including
                     a description of Satan's physical appearance (fols. 87vb-88vb)
 II) Malkǝʾa
                     Mikāʾel "Image of Michael" (fols. 88vb-92vb) (cp. ChRep no. 119)
 
                     Colophon.</summary>
