                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#92vb">92vb</locus>: ተፈጸመ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በእደ፡ ጸሐፌሁ፡ ቄስ፡ ደስታ፡
                        ገ/ማርያም፡ ዘብሔረ፡ ልጋት፡ በ፲ወ፱፻፷ወ፭ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት። ወተሣየጦ፡ በ፹ወ፭ብሩር፡ [vac.] ወወሀቦ፡ ለታቦተ፡ ማርያም፡
                        ዓዲ፡ ቀያሕቶ። ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ ውጉዘ፡ ለይኩን፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጲጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ ወአሜን፡
                        ለይኩን፡ ለይኩን።This book was completed by the hand of the scribe priest Dästa Gabra
                        Māryām from the land of Lǝgat in the year of mercy 1965. [vac.] He has
                        purchased it for 85 Bǝrr and donated it to the church of Mary ʿAddi Qiyaḥto.
                        The one who stole it or erased (its text) shall be excommunicated by the
                        authority of Peter and Paul. For ever and ever. Amen and amen. Let it be, let
                        it be. The year of mercy 1965 corresponds to 1972/73 A.D. The space for the
                        name of the commissioner has been left unfilled (?). </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  
